profile.bio:
Born in Torun, Poland - the famed birthplace of the great astronomer, Nicholas Copernicus. Also famous for amazing honey-cakes.

Came to Canada in 1980. Graduated from Electrical Engineering at U of C in 1993. Have worked with software since then.
